Convert the ssh server stuff from prototype code to tested code.

Make a github plugin to get PR and github events.

Make a changeset that knows about the source of the change.

Get jobs to run from the changeset. It should parse .bard.yml

Put the jobs in a job queue.

Have an executor pool.

Each executor has host details.

Make a scheduler that takes jobs, matches them with executors, and runs them.

When all jobs for a changeset have been run, update the changeset.

Changeset updates the source of the change.